    <name>ROT Management GUI</name>
    <summary>A GUI to manage RPM-OSTree Systems</summary>

    <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
    <project_license>GPL-3.0-only</project_license>

    <description>
        <p>ROT Management GUI is a user-friendly graphical interface for managing RPM-OSTree
            systems, designed to help users who are not experienced with the command line interface
            maintain their atomic Linux distributions like Fedora Silverblue and Kinoite.</p>
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> For this app to work correctly you MUST disable automatic
            updates in GNOME Software/KDE Software Update. Check this in GNOME Software -
            Preferences or KDE Settings - Software Update.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Update your system and Flatpak applications</li>
            <li>Rollback your system in case anything goes wrong</li>
            <li>Pin and unpin deployments</li>
            <li>View all your system deployments</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

